* Wu Hung: What is Bianxiang? - On The Relationship Between Dunhuang Art and Dunhuang Literature. Harvard Journal of Asiatic Studies, Vol. 52, No. 1 (Jun., 1992), pp. 111-192. [[@http://www.jstor.org/stable/2719330.|JSTOR]] 
