* Denise Patry Leidy: The Ssu-Wei Figure in Sixth-Century A.D. Chinese Buddhist Sculpture. Archives of Asian Art , Vol. 43 (1990): 21-37 [[@http://www.jstor.org/stable/20111204|JSTOR]] 
